 that love and family are worth keeping in this powerful, emotional, and hopeful novel"--cProvided by publisher. 0aBreastxCancerxPatientsvFiction. 0aBuildingsxRepair and reconstructionvFiction. 0aFamily secretsvFiction. 0aLarge type books. 0aOklahoma City (Okla.)vFiction. 0aWashington (State)vFiction. 7aDomestic fiction.2lcgft  c(OCoLC)1225192940  aREADY FOR QC  c4731d4731